Psychometric paper outlining the development of a multidimensional measure of divorced parent concerns. 

Recommended citation: Sanford, K., & Rivers, A. S. (2017). The Parting Parent Concern Inventory: Parents’ appraisals correlate with divorced family functioning. Journal of Family Psychology, 31(7), 867-877. http://doi.org/10.1037/fam0000340
